{"tid":997101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國製頂尖軍用雷達失效 台議員：根本垃圾","createTime":"2019-01-27T00:21:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T13:26:13.000Z","uid":177089,"like":281,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"5a10fa547e3a98e28ee7afbfc9a03a9cc457fcbb","tid":997101,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T00:21:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E9%9B%B7%E9%81%94%E8%A2%AB%E7%82%B8%E6%AF%80-%E4%BB%96-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%BB%8D%E6%AD%A6%E5%AF%A6%E6%88%B0%E5%83%8F%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE-030024154.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E9%259B%25B7%25E9%2581%2594%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%2582%25B8%25E6%25AF%2580-%25E4%25BB%2596-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25BB%258D%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E6%2588%25B0%25E5%2583%258F%25E5%259E%2583%25E5%259C%25BE-030024154.html&d=VUGLEaUORJJ7MxxoyUgS9QRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=f905dc7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E9%9B%B7%E9%81%94%E8%A2%AB%E7%82%B8%E6%AF%80-%E4%BB%96-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%BB%8D%E6%AD%A6%E5%AF%A6%E6%88%B0%E5%83%8F%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE-030024154.html</a><br />\n<br />\n以色列空軍日前出動F-16成功空襲敘利亞軍隊在大馬士革國際機場部署的雷達基地，<span style=\"color: red;\">摧毀</span>俄羅斯製的Pantsir-S1（鎧甲-S1）防空系統及<span style=\"color: red;\">中國製的JY-27雷達</span>。對此，桃園市議員王浩宇表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">中國號稱JY-27雷達能探測到以色列空軍的F-35隱形戰鬥機，但實戰時卻連F-16都偵測不到，「中國軍武，實戰就像垃圾。」</span><br />\n<br />\n王浩宇在臉書上表示，以色列日前針對敘利亞首都大馬士革軍事目標進行摧毀行動，<span style=\"color: red;\">僅派出F-16戰機就順利炸毀了最先進的中國隱身雷達</span>及俄國防空系統。其中，中國最先進的JY-27雷達，號稱對空最大探測距離達300公里，能探測到以色列空軍的F-35隱形戰鬥機，但實戰時卻連F-16都偵測不到，<span style=\"color: red;\">慘遭以色列空軍F-16戰機摧毀，證明中國軍武根本毫無實用性</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uMhZLWK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuMhZLWK.png&h=ee431a47&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xYyuoJp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxYyuoJp.png&h=8e9c2e0c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2eb103a83ee85b209b31e294fb6d2bcdd70b9c8","tid":997101,"uid":103230,"like":179,"dislike":0,"score":179,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T00:25:08.000Z","msg":"屌f16都偵測唔倒真係好過份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80a7d0897735ca203e2c097377fd01d7eb01fd95","tid":997101,"uid":35136,"like":120,"dislike":1,"score":119,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T00:27:22.000Z","msg":"五毛：用家問題"},{"pid":"ad5da94de12e0949f1efb1932535520fa1cda547","tid":997101,"uid":52215,"like":5,"dislike":167,"score":-162,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T00:31:52.000Z","msg":"雷達唔識擊落戰機架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05a220ed1410c34f223c80fc13b10e256e4aeb72","tid":997101,"uid":177089,"like":300,"dislike":3,"score":297,"quote":{"pid":"ad5da94de12e0949f1efb1932535520fa1cda547","tid":997101,"uid":52215,"like":5,"dislike":167,"score":-162,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T00:31:52.000Z","msg":"雷達唔識擊落戰機架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T00:36:53.000Z","msg":"就等緊你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n王浩宇說，至於俄羅斯製的Pantsir-S1（鎧甲-S1）防空系統，則<span style=\"color: red;\">因為中國製雷達預警太慢，雖然射出部分飛彈，但沒有攔截到任何導彈就全遭殲滅</span>"},{"pid":"ba3b47fcaa4888e3d87861bcf7333fc4f96e6bbb","tid":997101,"uid":61967,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"05a220ed1410c34f223c80fc13b10e256e4aeb72","tid":997101,"uid":177089,"like":300,"dislike":3,"score":297,"quote":{"pid":"ad5da94de12e0949f1efb1932535520fa1cda547","tid":997101,"uid":52215,"like":5,"dislike":167,"score":-162,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T00:31:52.000Z","msg":"雷達唔識擊落戰機架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T00:36:53.000Z","msg":"就等緊你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/d